data_table.name: HVH_Subject_Phenotypes
data_table.description: This subject phenotype data table includes case control status, index year, race, ethnicity, age, sex, height, weight, stroke type, venous thrombosis type, echocardiographic measurements at AF onset (n=2 variables; left atrial diameter and ejection fraction <50%), treated diseases (n=3 variables; hypertension, diabetes milletus, and hyperlipidemia), and smoking status.
